&uuml;&ccedil;in hassany d&uuml;&yacute;pli g&ouml;zlemek
ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&Uuml;ns&uuml;&#328; ulgamla&yacute;yn
keselleri&#328;, damar kesellerini&#328;, gyzzyrma epizodlaryny&#328;, arterial
gipertoni&yacute;any&#328;, s&uuml;&yacute;ji keselini&#328; &yacute;a-da
&yacute;aramaz d&uuml;w&uuml;rtikleri&#328;, prostata m&auml;zini&#328;
kesellerini&#328;, uroliti&yacute;azy&#328; bolmagyna &uuml;nsi
&ccedil;ek&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Angiotensini &ouml;wr&uuml;ji ferment
ingibitorlaryny&#328;, steroid d&auml;l &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y
dermanlary&#328;, aminoglikozidleri&#328; we rentgen kontrast
seri&#351;delerini&#328; orna&#351;dyrylmagyna a&yacute;ratyn &uuml;ns
beril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Z&auml;herli, z&auml;herli maddalar bilen
aragatna&#351;ygy, my&#351;salary&#328; zeperlenmegini&#328; alamatlaryny,
metabolik keselleri&#328; bardygyny, ge&ccedil;mi&#351;de kreatini&#328; we
karbamidi&#328; k&ouml;pelmegini anyklamaly.&nbsp;Lukman hassany g&ouml;zden
ge&ccedil;irende derini&#328; we gyjyndyrmalary&#328; re&#328;kine,
d&ouml;k&uuml;lmeleri&#328;, suwsuzlygy&#328; derejesine, &ouml;demi&#328;
barlygyna, agzyndan ammiak ysyna baha ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bedeni&#328;
temperaturasyny &ouml;l&ccedil;&yacute;&auml;rler, &ouml;&yacute;kenleri
di&#328;le&yacute;&auml;rler, gan basy&#351;yny we impulsyny
&ouml;l&ccedil;&yacute;&auml;rler, bagry&#328;, b&ouml;wrekleri&#328; we
&ouml;t haltany&#328; ululygyny kesgitlemek &uuml;&ccedil;in garyn bo&#351;lugyny
(du&yacute;&yacute;arlar), &#351;e&yacute;le hem n&auml;sagy&#328; nerw
ulgamyny&#328; &yacute;agda&yacute;yna baha ber&yacute;&auml;rler.</span></p>

